{"tid":516332,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地分左手後，點樣改造自己成為一個唔同的人？","createTime":"2018-01-01T10:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T14:15:46.000Z","uid":18626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5f75dfc2d801e283e090b8262420fbd907886ee9","tid":516332,"uid":18626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:18:56.000Z","msg":"俗語有云：分一次，醒一次<br />\n當你地經歷分手，點樣改造自己，重新做人。<br />\n<br />\n未必係分左手，受過挫折的bro都可以分享你地點樣改造自己。<br />\n<br />\n我就會做gym,睇落個人好睇少少。"},{"pid":"c66fea6b2ec8086b37356e061c11e8b614bdd61e","tid":516332,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:20:11.000Z","msg":"對衣著有多啲要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a99948aef86ec373337dcc46984d9fda19ef195","tid":516332,"uid":5077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/01/182939_f576f2fd87b8185f18ba301b21f89bfb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F01%2F182939_f576f2fd87b8185f18ba301b21f89bfb.jpeg&h=ecfb5b32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"419765fe17634860b998615ee028dab0db5bae8f","tid":516332,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:31:17.000Z","msg":"多數係做返啲好撚正面嘅事<br />\n玩多樣活動<br />\n上個Course呀之類"},{"pid":"dd89fd77f06a00394b22bd037a88c1d0d2a7b22d","tid":516332,"uid":131214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"唔會因為要去交往去做多啲野改變自己<br />\n相對地<br />\n亦唔會因為分手而有咩嘢打擊要去改變自己<br />\n我本如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似進修/運動呢啲類, 就算結合還是分手<br />\n; 呢啲做咗對你本身都有好處<br />\n唔係為咗邊個/咩原因去做"},{"pid":"69e98da207f77cb8eeea79ad6ce0e0e11b55360c","tid":516332,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"狂叫雞"},{"pid":"dd7f7160b89f8e39a7bc5094477836319dd100f3","tid":516332,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:12:17.000Z","msg":"做自己<br />\n同佢黎之前一樣<br />\n同佢走之前一樣<br />\n當中嘅砂石同空隙就任由時間去填補<br />\n<br />\n越係刻意越係動彈不得"},{"pid":"77d4d17ea380d9af265de576d43fdcbc2c41dd33","tid":516332,"uid":7599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:15:02.000Z","msg":"一邊令自己開心<br />\n另一邊又自己傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c46776b16d8a95ca5b6fc2987fb88aae4dfaef4","tid":516332,"uid":83063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"變得似翻個男人  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前份人好廢<br />\n係街同人嘈都會驚<br />\n<br />\n分左手之後<br />\n<br />\n會聲大大同人講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28467f7af81865f9ec9a419ec21051869b601f4","tid":516332,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:01:42.000Z","msg":"條件差唔代表佢會對自己好啲<br />\n就好似：九把刀/ 吹波波<br />\n柒頭都會出軌<br />\n我不如揀個好樣既"},{"pid":"9f9da99950d4bae57717dd2c7df30a89a01580fa","tid":516332,"uid":73238,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"第一次分手<br />\n我知自己圈子窄 我擴闊左自己圈子<br />\n<br />\n第二次分手<br />\n其實冇咩好改造 但就知道拍拖有啲位要避忌下<br />\n<br />\n第三次分手<br />\n我感覺自己成熟左 自信心多左 <br />\n<br />\n最主要係初戀 冇初戀我可能唔會由一個毒撚變到呢家咁"},{"pid":"5951b49478cd4b389d82c53c02809661fa128143","tid":516332,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:23:06.000Z","msg":"點解要突登變做另一個人<br />\n襯呢個時間多啲認識了解吓自己唔係仲好"},{"pid":"4ffc470c288b9326d69ed6e8d211a905613d4ff3","tid":516332,"uid":143307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"唔再軟弱 變得成熟<br />\n唔會再經常喊"}]}